#19 - info - SELECT p.id as id,
		                   p.slug as slug,
		                   p.name as name,
		                   p.completed_on as completed_on,
		                   p.leader_id as leader_id,
		                   MIN(o.date_field_1) as start_on,
		                   MAX(o.due_on) as due_on
		                   FROM
		                   acx_projects as p
		                   LEFT JOIN acx_project_objects as o ON o.project_id = p.id AND o.type = 'Milestone' AND o.state = '3'
		                   WHERE p.id IN ('1', '2')
		                   AND p.state = '3'
		                   GROUP BY id
		                   ORDER BY start_on ASC
